step 1:
Signup
method Post: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/signup
body > form-data
username:
password:
* example *
username: abra
password: 123456

step 2:
Login
method Post: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/login
body > form-data
username:
password:

step 3:
Write message
method Post: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages
body > form-data
receiver:
subject:
message:
* example *
receiver: 1
subject: Hi
message: hello word

step 4:
Get all messages
method Get: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages

step 5:
Get all message by id
method Get: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages/<input_message_id>
* example *
method Get: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages/3
- NOTE - if you sand a Get request.
 note that "READ" = FALSE,
 if you sand another get request it will turn as TRUE.


step 6:
Delete message
method Delete: https://messages-app-abra.herokuapp.com/messages/<input_message_id>